OL,6,FWATCH: ITV Meridian's Tom Savvides
OL,7,Freports on those shining a light on
OL,8,Fthe devastating disease Noma. He spoke
OL,9,Fto Mulikat Okanlawon, a survivor and
OL,10,Fcampaigner from Nigeria.
OL,12,FIt's a gangrenous infection which can
OL,13,Fdestroy the face in a matter of weeks
OL,14,Fbut few people have heard of Noma.
OL,16,FIt was officially listed by the World
OL,17,FHealth Organisation as a neglected
OL,18,Ftropical disease in 2023, and occurs
OL,19,Fin poverty-stricken areas of Africa.
