OL,6,FIt's fatal in 90% of cases, and
OL,7,Fsurvivors are left with severe
OL,8,Fdisfigurement causing pain, discomfort
OL,9,Fand stigma.
OL,11,FOne of those fighting to highlight the
OL,12,Fdisease is Mulikat Okanlawon from
OL,13,FNigeria, who not only survived noma,
OL,14,Fbut went on to co-found Elysium, the
OL,15,Ffirst noma survivors' association.
