OL,6,FShe's regarded as one of Time
OL,7,FMagazine's 100 most influential people
OL,8,Fin global health, and she's helped to
OL,9,Fproduce a documentary, which was
OL,10,Fscreened to students at the Brighton
OL,11,Fand Sussex Medical School.
OL,13,FRestoring Dignity tells her story and
OL,14,Foffers a glimpse into other survivors'
OL,15,Flives too, following their struggles
OL,16,Fand achievements over the course of a
OL,17,Fyear.
OL,19,FThe event took place to mark World
OL,20,FNeglected Tropical Diseases Day on
OL,21,FJanuary 30.
