OL,6,F"I just want people to know about it,"
OL,7,Fshe said, " to know how to support and
OL,8,Fto know how to love this survivor and
OL,9,Fto take care of them, to lose the
OL,10,Fstigma and help them live an
OL,11,Findependent life."
OL,13,FResearchers at the medical school are
OL,14,Fcarrying out studies into tropical
OL,15,Fskin diseases, which often affect the
OL,16,Fmost vulnerable and marginalised
OL,17,Fpeople.
OL,19,FThey aim to provide treatments, cures
OL,20,Fand possibly future vaccines for
OL,21,Fsevere infections.
