OL,6,FGem Aellah, a research fellow at the
OL,7,Fmedical school said: "The voices of
OL,8,Fpeople who are affected by these
OL,9,Freally stigmatising neglected diseases
OL,10,Fare often really marginalised.
OL,12,F"So they're not often heard in
OL,13,Fpolicymaking. They're not often heard
OL,14,Fin public forums like this."
